{"tid":1869104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎：患者家屬講述艱難就醫路，無法確診死後迅速火化","createTime":"2020-02-08T03:46:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T04:32:12.000Z","uid":56533,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7c37fd926194ac461287e6aa2a6fad6445934d40","tid":1869104,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:46:01.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情仍然嚴峻，兩名新型冠狀病毒肺炎的患者家屬與BBC記者沙磊（John Sudworth）對話，講述自己親屬求醫的艱難經歷。<br />\n<br />\n小黃（化名）的爺爺花了九天時間才看到病，但在獲得一張難求的醫院牀位後不久便去世了。另一名患者家屬王文君說，她的大伯被送入隔離酒店後不久便身亡，他的父親如今也病入膏肓。<br />\n<br />\n片: <a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-51411732\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-51411732&d=KH9yB5wEnJvJbT5Qn4WrOvsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=b162c767\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fchinese-news-51411732&h=98ab1cb8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/chinese-news-51411732</a>"},{"pid":"3ffebeb1fdf62e823ea7a81593e2d43849a8aa1e","tid":1869104,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T03:57:25.000Z","msg":"咁樣死既支那狗唔辛確診，又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd0a673ae01842768e13cbc4d3effab021602aa7","tid":1869104,"uid":274772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:02:18.000Z","msg":"單係呢點,已100%證明死亡人數可把官方數字加3個0"},{"pid":"d6d19ce89050984953ca07afaa1ba7998da73105","tid":1869104,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:07:32.000Z","msg":"中國近幾年扮曬太平盛世<br />\n呢個就係真面目"},{"pid":"583bfd7741c7d15dd23ef71aff7f9759a190ee78","tid":1869104,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:15:12.000Z","msg":"仲好啦，自焚慳返美國粒核彈"},{"pid":"1594df92561426ede23762be8e1de88c65c8644f","tid":1869104,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-08T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"要實現2.1死亡率，的確